videos.description: Tennessee big man Kyle Alexander runs the floor and is rewarded with a pass and a huge finish.
videos.headline: Alexander runs the floor and throws down thunderous jam

videos.description: Tennessee guard Lamonte Turner drives down the lane and puts in the scoop layup at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Turner hits layup at the first-half buzzer

videos.description: Tennessee runs the out of bounds play to perfection and Jordan Bone finds John Fulkerson for the alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Fulkerson throws it down off the lob

videos.description: Admiral Schofield scores 18 points in his last home game to lead Tennessee to a 71-54 victory over Mississippi State.
